There

efficiency
this

The

Due
the

most

Audio
Signal

the

each

this

the

Yes

good

audio

and
has
been
traditional

for
speaker

you
want
better

than

buy

even
exists
The

just

Audiophiles

and
with

it's
just
not

extra
What
important

you
use
heavy
enough
gauge
wire
Heavy

speaker
wire
more
durable
better
insulated
and
will
carry
heavier

over
longer
distances
with
less
signal
loss
lower
resistance
For

gauge
fine
like
gauge
because
know
will
endure
the
pitfalls
home
use
such
being
nibbled
the

such
The

not

gauge

wire

that's
with
For

this
wire
easily
soldered

regular
rosin

not

Instead
